snippet.title: Dandara Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.dandaragame.com

In a bizarre universe where the oppressed are on the brink of oblivion, Dandara has awoken to bring balance to this directionless world. Dandara launches the week of February 6 for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, PC, iOS and Android.
